## Setup Instructions

```bash
# 1. Install dependencies
pip install -e .
pip install -e ".[dev]"

# 2. Configure environment
cp .env.example .env
# Edit .env with local config

# 3. Initialize database
alembic revision -m "baseline"
alembic upgrade head

# 4. Run application
uvicorn app.main:app --reload

# 5. Test
curl http://localhost:8000/health
pytest tests/
```

## Dependencies Requirements

For full functionality, ensure these services are running:
- PostgreSQL (default: localhost:5432)
- Redis (default: localhost:6379)
- MinIO (default: localhost:9000)

Health endpoint will report "degraded" if any dependency is unavailable.
